title: 127. 2 Distinct Championship Caliber Qualities
itunes:title: 127. 2 Distinct Championship Caliber Qualities
description:
Most people are stuck in the cycle of executing for a few days and then sabotaging their progress by “rewarding themselves.” On today’s episode, Andy explains how all the great things in your life come from creating momentum, why it is extremely important to keep it going and how you can force positive momentum in your life to achieve all your goals.

  • Get my raw & uncensored advice about success & life delivered to you daily!
